caption.p: The inhibitory activity of NC-5 on influenza A virus neuraminidase (NA). ( A) NA-inhibitory effect on A/FM/1/47 (H1N1) and A/FM/1/47-H275Y (H1N1-H275Y). ( B) A/Beijing/32/92 (H3N2). ( C) A/Anhui/1/2013 (H7N9) and A/Anhui/1/2013-R294K (H7N9-R294K). ( D) A/Vietnam/1203/2004 (H5N1). Oseltamivir carboxylate (OC) (1 nM) was used as a positive control. The results are represented as the mean Â± S.D. of three independent experiments, * p <0.05, ** p <0.01, *** p <0.001, compared with the dimethyl sulfoxide (DMSO) control.
